<p class="ayah 57-13" id="13" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(On the) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَقُولُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will say</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُنَـٰفِقُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the hypocrite men</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْمُنَـٰفِقَـٰتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the hypocrite women</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱنظُرُونَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Wait for us,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَقْتَبِسْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">we may acquire</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُّورِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your light.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">It will be said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱرْجِعُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Go back</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَرَآءَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">behind you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱلْتَمِسُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and seek</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُورًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">light.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَضُرِبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then will be put up</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْنَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">between them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِسُورٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a wall,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَابُۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a gate</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَاطِنُهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">its interior,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرَّحْمَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) mercy</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَظَـٰهِرُهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but its exterior,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن قِبَلِهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">facing towards [it]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَذَابُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the punishment.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>13<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
